elements.name: As an OpenMRS user I want to test login and find a patient record So that the system works as expected
Positive Case - Finding a valid patient record

the user clicks on Find Patient Record
the user should be directed to "OpenMRS Electronic Medical Record" page
the user enters patient name and click on details
the user should see a record with patient name
